data.description: Rare opportunity to see a listing in Glenmont Estates. Home of tree lined streets & split rail fences!  SIX Large Bedrooms, FIVE full baths + Den. Master Bedroom retreat w/sitting room. ENJOY your PRIVATE pool, Built in BBQ with sink & Gas Firepit! Kitchen Upgrades include Granite counter tops, double oven, gas stove, Gorgeous Espresso Kitchen Cabinets with crown molding. Upgraded oil rubbed bronze fixtures throughout, ceiling fans and recent interior painting. Exterior includes RV Gate, Extended patio with pool fence. The Community offers walking paths, lush green common areas with playground, basketball court & Ramada's for residents only! GREAT location close to Spring Training Goodyear Ballpark, Goodyear Recreation Campus, Harkins Theater, Goodyear Civic Square Entertainment Hub, shopping and restaurants! Welcome to Goodyear! AZ Cardinals State Farm stadium, Entertainment -Sports Venues/downtown Phoenix all within 25 miles. Great highway interstate access 303 and I-10. Leased Solar Panels to cut down on utility bill! Separate Living room and Great room.  Rare opportunity to find a six bedroom and full five bath home! . Recent improvements: new coils to AC, dishwasher, electric panel updated with all new breakers, new drip system hub.
